videos.headline: Mathews' hurdle leads to Pittsburgh TD
videos.description: Pittsburgh QB Kenny Pickett tosses a pass to WR Aaron Mathews who hurdles a defender for a 24-yard pass play. RB A.J. Davis follows up with a 2-yard touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mathews' hurdle leads to Pittsburgh TD) 2019/09/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pitt's Pickett finds Ffrench for TD
videos.description: Pittsburgh QB Kenny Pickett quickly passes to WR Maurice Ffrench, who finds his way into the end zone for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pitt's Pickett finds Ffrench for TD) 2019/09/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pitt's Pinnock races over for interception
videos.description: UCF QB Dillon Gabriel lobs a pass to WR Jacob Harris in the end zone, but Pittsburgh DB Jason Pinnock speeds over to make a leaping interception.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pitt's Pinnock races over for interception) 2019/09/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pitt returns blocked punt for TD
videos.description: Pittsburgh's Aaron Mathews comes in and blocks Andrew Osteen's punt and Wendell Davis returns it 18 yards for a Panthers' touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pitt returns blocked punt for TD) 2019/09/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Killins Jr. gets UCF on the board with TD run
videos.description: UCF RB Adrian Killins Jr. rushes 11 yards into the end zone to give the Knights their first touchdown of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Killins Jr. gets UCF on the board with TD run) 2019/09/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: UCF's Davis left uncovered for TD
videos.description: Pittsburgh gets caught in busted coverage as UCF QB Dillon Gabriel finds an uncovered WR Gabriel Davis for the touchdown to cut the Panthers' lead to 21-17.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UCF's Davis left uncovered for TD) 2019/09/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Anderson gives UCF the lead with 87-yard punt return TD
videos.description: Otis Anderson catches the punt and returns it 87 yards to the house to give the Knights a 24-21 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Anderson gives UCF the lead with 87-yard punt return TD) 2019/09/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Narduzzi calls game-winning play 'Pitt Special'
videos.description: Pittsburgh head coach Pat Narduzzi says the Panthers' game-winning play against UCF was "Pitt Special," and commends his player's execution to pull off the upset.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Narduzzi calls game-winning play 'Pitt Special') 2019/9/21

videos.headline: Relive Pitt's game-winning TD from the fans' view in the seats
videos.description: Rewatch from multiple angles Pitt's game-winning touchdown pass to end UCF's 27-game regular season win streak.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Relive Pitt’s game-winning TD from the fans' view in the seats) 2019/09/21 ESHEET
